{"tid":751757,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(同大劉嘈交) 大陸登台成年練好普通話  Diva許珮榆希望喺香港拍戲","createTime":"2018-07-22T07:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T10:17:15.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b0b38fd6a6bfa9337c560e356229683bbdc478","tid":751757,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"日前喺銅鑼灣希慎廣場，同大劉劉鑾雄口角，繼而被大劉指罵係整容怪物，兼整容N次嘅許珮榆（Diva），因為今次邊行路邊睇手機，引致護子心切嘅大劉，怕Diva撞到其兒女而緊張提點，豈料變成相方街頭口舌爭辯，被指整容怪物嘅Diva更表示，當時向大劉表示話可以即刻去驗，問大劉如果佢冇整容，係唔係賠錢俾佢，無論誰是誰非，夠膽喺街頭同大劉唇槍舌劍，兼討價還價嘅人都真係罕有少見。<br />\n<br />\nDiva日前於清水灣為本報拍攝夏季水着，現年27歲，擁有混血樣子嘅許珮榆（Diva），祖父係葡萄牙人，外婆係新疆人，2009年拍攝TVB青春劇《四葉草-南華夢飛翔》出道，曾簽約模特公司成為陳靜（DaDa）師妹，2013年曾推出寫真《華麗美少女》，2016曾參加ViuTV選美節目《美選D.n.A》，曾參與多齣電影演出，現在活躍大陸登同東南亞登台演出，簽約大陸公司，Diva稱一年大概有50場演出，主要係唱歌同負責DJ打碟。<br />\n<br />\nDiva成年都喺全大陸不同城巿登台獻唱，練得一口流利普通話，就連飲歌都係大陸最hit嘅歌，Diva話：「自己都希望有自己嘅歌推出，在大陸工作算辛苦，試過到茂名，沒有飛機直達，要坐車6小時，試過尿急都唔敢去大陸街上嘅洗手間，要較為乾淨先至夠膽去。」展望將來，Diva希望喺香港有機會拍電影，佢話：「希望喺香港拍電影，喺大陸工作耐咗，想多點時間留喺香港發展。」<br />\n<br />\nDiva年前搭港鐵時遇上不愉快事件，當時被非禮卻沒有報警，咁啱得咁橋，又係被人影到佢同一名大叔嘈交，Diva回想：「網上有短片流傳我喺地鐵同一個阿叔嘈交，其實係一年前發生，當時自己穿着露腰上衫，個大叔大斷用手摸我、非禮我，我退後叫佢唔好再摸，佢唔認，又話唔小心撞到我，我叫佢講對唔住，佢唔肯，我實在忍好耐，因為趕住去做嘢冇報警，我想呼籲，作為女性一定唔可以驚，一定要出聲，我下次一定會追究到底。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151203_f9f750f7fc26ae141a303df47719425f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151203_f9f750f7fc26ae141a303df47719425f.jpg&h=f6574bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151204_1ba69542d978607e73af8c72541dbdce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151204_1ba69542d978607e73af8c72541dbdce.jpg&h=1d53a26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151204_ffa63b94c47f6039cc354193cf5dd466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151204_ffa63b94c47f6039cc354193cf5dd466.jpg&h=f92c1375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151204_079a2147fa4504ab2f218707952263b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151204_079a2147fa4504ab2f218707952263b7.jpg&h=d53c4c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151205_07d9a6bfbaa27777cb750ff59e03d200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151205_07d9a6bfbaa27777cb750ff59e03d200.jpg&h=db6e4429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151205_bff45bddfebb5e8d650c64ce2ca6e4e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151205_bff45bddfebb5e8d650c64ce2ca6e4e2.jpg&h=a22f3b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有專訪, 睇黎越來越多job接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178806220c023ef8a544742a5929dd55da710e1","tid":751757,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰 我信佢冇整"},{"pid":"5456ed5cd11141c760ab84170a65b48aa9a63609","tid":751757,"uid":156068,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23519a1ca40a81b663a1d476a436f25355fcab27","tid":751757,"uid":48905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"快撚Ｄ捧紅佢添呀"},{"pid":"455438de19b6d7bcc5a828e07cb8ed8c7830411c","tid":751757,"uid":22633,"like":9,"disl